This change log only focus on changes in the application of the python package.
Consider the commit messages for changes on the code basis or additions to the
package.

Since 2017-01-03 (3ec99cdc4c247dc54bfddd30fa9469bea809852d):
- getCellsAlongLine( Rs, phis, Zs, Grid ) is renamed to 
  getCellIndex( points, Grid ). It can be easily transfered by defining points 
  as zip( Rs, phis, Zs ).

Since 2016-07-08 (b699d7539bcb94807ec14c2f2f597675311c8494):
- Data from an object A of class PlasmaField previously accessed via 
  A[ quantity ][1] need to be accessed via A( quantity ).